About Us
American Restaurant in Leesburg, FL
At Ramshackle Cafe, we’re all about providing our guests with a casual and welcoming dining experience. We’re the kind of place where you can come in for a quick bite to eat, or linger over a meal with friends.
Our
menu
features a variety of delicious options, from classic American comfort food to more creative and international dishes. And of course, we have a full bar, so you can enjoy a cocktail or beer with your meal.
We’re also known for our friendly service and convenient location. Our bar is in the middle of the restaurant, so it’s easy to grab a drink while you’re waiting for your food.
Join Us for Breakfast, Lunch, or Dinner!
Whether you’re a local or just passing through, we hope you’ll come and see us at Ramshackle Cafe. Serving
breakfast, lunch, and dinner
—we’re your neighborhood spot for delicious food, great drinks, and a good time! Visit our restaurant in Leesburg, FL today.
Local Roots. Nationwide Inspiration.
While we draw inspiration from coast to coast, our heart remains in Leesburg. We pride ourselves on sourcing local ingredients, championing sustainability, and celebrating Florida’s rich bounty.
